===Real Madrid===
====2009-13: Kutumiza dziko lonse ndi La Liga====
Pambuyo pa nyengo ya 2009-10, Ronaldo adagwirizanitsa Real Madrid ndi ndalama zokwana £ 80 miliyoni (€ 94 miliyoni). Msonkhano wake, umene unapitilira mpaka 2015, unali wokwanira € 11 miliyoni pachaka ndipo unali ndi chigamulo chogulitsa € 1 biliyoni. Mafilimu okwana 80,000 adapezeka ku Santiago Bernabéu, kupitirira zaka 25 za mafilimu 75,000 omwe adalandira Diego Maradona ku Napoli. Ronaldo adalandira sheti ya nambala 9, yomwe idaperekedwa kwa iye yemwe anali mtsogoleri wa Madrid, Alfredo Di Stéfano.

[[File:Cristiano Ronaldo Madrid.jpg|thumb|upright|left|Monga momwe chiwerengero chake chokhalira 7 sichinali kupezeka, Ronaldo ankavala nambala 9 m'nyengo yake yoyamba ku Madrid. Raúl atachoka, Ronaldo anapatsidwa satifiketi 7 patsogolo pake [[2010–11 La Liga|Nyengo ya 2010-11]].]]

Ronaldo adayamba ku [[La Liga]] pa 29 August 2009, motsutsana ndi [[Deportivo de La Coruña|Deportivo La Coruña]], ndipo adapeza malo otsekedwa ku chipinda cha 3-2 cha Madrid.<ref>{{cite news |title=Ronaldo akugonjetsa Real |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8229070.stm |publisher=BBC Sport |date=29 August 2009 |accessdate=29 August 2009}}</ref> Iye adalemba muzitsulo zake zonse zoyambilira ndi klabu, mchenga woyamba wa Madrid kuti achite zimenezo.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/players/cristiano-ronaldo/6225577/Cristiano-Ronaldo-makes-Real-Madrid-history.html |title=Cristiano Ronaldo amapanga mbiri ya Real Madrid |work=The Daily Telegraph |location=London |date=23 September 2009 |accessdate=25 August 2010}}</ref>

===Juventus===
====2018–19====
Pambuyo pa sabata imodzi yowonongeka, pa July 10, 2018, Ronaldo adasainira mgwirizano wa zaka zinayi ndi chigamulo cha Italiya Juventus atamaliza ndalama zokwana € 100 miliyoni, kuphatikizapo ndalama zothandizana ndi magulu a achinyamata a Ronaldo ndi € 12 miliyoni zina.<ref>{{cite press release |title=Cristiano Ronaldo akuimira Juventus!|url=http://www.juventus.com/en/news/news/2018/cristiano-ronaldo-signs-for-juventus.php |website=juventus.com |date=10 July 2018}}</ref>  Kusamutsidwa kunali kwapamwamba kwambiri kwa wosewera mpira wazaka zoposa 30,<ref>{{cite news |title=Cristiano Ronaldo ku Juventus: Kodi £ 99m atsegula ndalama zabwino kwa akatswiri a ku Italy?|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44785738 |accessdate=10 July 2018 |agency=BBC}}</ref> ndipo wapamwamba kwambiri omwe adalandiridwa ndi chipinda cha Italy. Ronaldo adanena kuti akufunika kuti adziwe ngati akufunika kuchoka pa Real Madrid. Ronaldo adagonjetsa Juventus pamsasa wawo wa Serie A pa 18 August, kupambana kwa Chimwevo 3-2.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.football-italia.net/126430/chievo-thriller-cr7-debut|title=Chievo zokondweretsa pa CR7 poyamba|publisher=Football Italia|date=18 August 2018}}</ref>

